<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #222;">
  <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px;">Upcoming Subscription Price Update</h2>
  <p>Hi <%= garage_name %>,</p>
  <p>
    We are updating your subscription price for the <strong><%= plan_name %></strong> plan.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Current price: <strong><%= old_price %></strong></li>
    <li>New price: <strong><%= new_price %></strong></li>
    <li>Effective on: <strong><%= effective_date %></strong></li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    If you wish to review or cancel before the effective date, visit your billing portal:
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="<%= billing_portal_url %>" style="background:#2d6cdf;color:#fff;padding:8px 12px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;">Open Billing Portal</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    For any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= support_email %>"><%= support_email %></a>.
  </p>
  <p>Thank you,<br/><%= app_name %></p>
</div>


